{"tid":491239,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載時事台新聞]撐Larva,罷買支那公司Zotac所有產品","createTime":"2017-12-06T10:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T10:49:11.000Z","uid":48234,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"23d653ad3f15bb79c4c91c281ff9431d29c0b6d2","tid":491239,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:16:32.000Z","msg":"在美國洛杉磯舉辦的索泰杯《星海爭霸》重製版錦標賽，中國選手羅賢慘遭韓國的Larva Afreeca羞辱，Larva在領先後做出用腳操作等嘲諷舉動，讓包括羅賢在內的中國人大怒，結果主辦方決定禁止Larva再參賽。<br />\n<br />\n據《香港01》報導，Larva在取得優勢，做出雙手交插操作、用腳操控等種種嘲諷的方式來繼續遊戲，對手羅賢則是事後才得知，憤怒在《微博》發文，痛斥Larva是小丑，「怎麼遇到這種腦子有病的人，你能從中獲得什麼樂趣或者為了積累到一些弱智粉絲。」Larva則反嗆自己已經得到主辦方允許，「如果你覺得被羞辱，我又沒有要你們看啊！」<br />\n<br />\n中國網友們崩潰要討公道，結果索泰回應表示，Larva羞辱對手的舉動不文明，也沒有向他所說的有向主辦方道歉，決定禁止Larva再參加索泰主辦的所有賽事。Larva得知後無奈表示，這個結果很令人沮喪。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171205/640_57c24700f4cdbd9cd04ff1fd541549e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171205%2F640_57c24700f4cdbd9cd04ff1fd541549e7.jpg&h=74bc36d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用腳玩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171205/640_1f4ba6674b41795f69572e98fec1f8d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171205%2F640_1f4ba6674b41795f69572e98fec1f8d8.jpg&h=be36a916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n交叉手玩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hSJM9qF0txw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhSJM9qF0txw&d=6ELBg8tlbAmHu5TpQmoco6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=a091458c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hSJM9qF0txw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20171205/1253734/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20171205%2F1253734%2F&d=6ELBg8tlbAmHu5TpQmoco6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h